聆听 The Gaslight Anthem 对 Billie Eilish 的《Ocean Eyes》的重磅翻唱https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-gaslight-anthems-heavy-cover-of-billie-eilishs-ocean-eyes-3608361?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=listen-to-比莉·艾利斯的《煤气灯下颂歌》重封面《海洋之眼》Anagricel Duran Fri, 22 Mar 2024 21:57:46 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3608361 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Gaslight-Anthem-and-Billie-Eilish.-Credit-Taylor-Hill-and-Matthew-Baker-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="煤气灯颂歌和比莉·艾利什。图片来源：泰勒·希尔 (Taylor Hill) 和马修·贝克 (Matthew Baker)，来源：GETTY" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Gaslight-Anthem-and-Billie-Eilish.-Credit-Taylor-Hill-and-Matthew-Baker-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Gaslight-Anthem-and-Billie-Eilish.-Credit-Taylor-Hill-and-Matthew-Baker-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Gaslight-Anthem-and-Billie-Eilish.-Credit-Taylor-Hill-and-Matthew-Baker-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Gaslight-Anthem-and-Billie-Eilish.-Credit-Taylor-Hill-and-Matthew-Baker-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Gaslight-Anthem-and-Billie-Eilish.-Credit-Taylor-Hill-and-Matthew-Baker-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Gaslight-Anthem-and-Billie-Eilish.-Credit-Taylor-Hill-and-Matthew-Baker-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>它出现在乐队的新 EP“History Books – Short Stories”中</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-gaslight-anthems-heavy-cover-of-billie-eilishs-ocean-eyes-3608361">《Listen to The Gaslight Anthem》对 Billie Eilish 的《Ocean Eyes》的厚重翻唱的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Gaslight-Anthem-and-Billie-Eilish.-Credit-Taylor-Hill-and-Matthew-Baker-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="煤气灯颂歌和比莉·艾利什。图片来源：泰勒·希尔 (Taylor Hill) 和马修·贝克 (Matthew Baker)，来源：GETTY" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Gaslight-Anthem-and-Billie-Eilish.-Credit-Taylor-Hill-and-Matthew-Baker-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Gaslight-Anthem-and-Billie-Eilish.-Credit-Taylor-Hill-and-Matthew-Baker-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Gaslight-Anthem-and-Billie-Eilish.-Credit-Taylor-Hill-and-Matthew-Baker-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Gaslight-Anthem-and-Billie-Eilish.-Credit-Taylor-Hill-and-Matthew-Baker-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Gaslight-Anthem-and-Billie-Eilish.-Credit-Taylor-Hill-and-Matthew-Baker-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Gaslight-Anthem-and-Billie-Eilish.-Credit-Taylor-Hill-and-Matthew-Baker-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/The-Gaslight-Anthem">《Gaslight Anthem》</a>重唱了<a href="/artists/Billie-Eilish">Billie Eilis</a>的《Ocean Eyes》。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/does-rock-n-roll-kill-braincells-the-gaslight-anthem-brian-fallon-3495130">摇滚乐会杀死脑细胞吗？！ ——《煤气灯颂歌》的布莱恩·法伦</a></strong></li></ul><p>新泽西摇滚乐队翻唱了 2016 年热门单曲，并作为她 2017 年 EP《Don&#39;t Smile At Me》的主打单曲，以令人难以忘怀的声音开始，然后直接跳入响亮的鼓点和突突的吉他声中，而主唱布莱恩·法伦 (Brian Fallon) 并置Eilish 原本柔和的嗓音加上他沙哑的声音。这首歌还由 psych-jam 贝斯手/乐队领队卡琳娜·莱克曼 (Karina Rykman) 演唱。</p><p>在一份声明中（通过<a href="https://www.stereogum.com/2256336/the-gaslight-anthem-ocean-eyes-billie-eilish-cover/music/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Stereogum</em></a> ）谈到他们决定翻唱《Ocean Eyes》时，法伦分享道：“我开车送女儿去学校，她在路上为我播放了这首歌，我真的很喜欢这首歌。然后有一天，我们和朋友们讨论封面的想法，我说，做一个更重版本的“Ocean Eyes”不是很酷吗？我尝试了一下，每个人都喜欢这个主意。” </p><p><iframe title="煤气灯颂歌 - 海洋之眼" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/wEjdOfsmNEA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>莱克曼在接受<a href="https://liveforlivemusic.com/news/gaslight-anthem-billie-eilish-ocean-eyes-karina-rykman-listen/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Live For Live Music</em></a>采访时谈到她参与翻唱的事情时说道：“布莱恩说他们正在翻唱比莉·艾利什，并问我是否想和他一起唱歌。显然我立即答应了！他太酷了，我喜欢结果。这张 EP 由 Butch Walker 制作，我喜欢他所做的声音决定。我很荣幸能够扮演一个小角色！”</p><p>该封面出现在《煤气灯之歌》的最新 EP“历史书籍 – 短篇小说”中。这张四首歌曲 EP 还收录了歌曲“Blue Jeans &amp; White T-Shirts”以及歌曲“Positive Charge”和“History Books”的原声版本。</p><p>这张 EP 是继他们 2023 年专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gaslight-anthem-share-history-books-feat-bruce-springsteen-and-announce-first-album-in-nine-years-3471572">History Books</a> 》之后推出的，这是他们九年来的第一张专辑。</p><p>在其他消息中，煤气灯圣歌目前正在进行英国和欧盟巡演。查看下面的剩余日期并<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fthe-gaslight-anthem-tickets%2Fartist%2F1282543" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处获取门票</a>。</p><h2> <strong>Gaslight Anthem 2024 英国和欧盟巡演日期为：</strong></h2><p><strong>行进</strong><br /><strong>23 – 伍尔弗汉普顿 – 大厅市政厅（英格兰）</strong><br /> <strong>25 – 伦敦 – 圆屋（英格兰）</strong><br /> <strong>26 – 伦敦 – 朗德豪斯（英格兰）</strong><br /> <strong>29 – 都柏林 – 3奥林匹亚剧院（爱尔兰共和国）</strong></p><p> <strong>2024 年 7 月</strong><br /><strong>10 - 诺丁汉 - 岩石城（英格兰）</strong><br /> <strong>11 – 切尔滕纳姆 – 2000Trees，Upcote 农场（英格兰）</strong></p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-gaslight-anthem-on-first-meeting-with-bruce-springsteen-i-freaked-out-3498727">主唱兼节奏吉他手布莱恩·法伦 (Brian Fallon) 讲述了他第一次见到新泽西州同胞布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀 (Bruce Springsteen) 的经历</a>。</p><p>法伦<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/does-rock-n-roll-kill-braincells-the-gaslight-anthem-brian-fallon-3495130">向<em>NME</em>回忆了</a>他对<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-161-1320368">斯普林斯汀在 2009 年格拉斯顿伯里加入乐队表演“The &#39;59 Sound”的</a>反应。</p><p> “我们的比赛还有 10 分钟，所以当他出现时，我无法思考，”法伦说。 “我的音乐专业大脑接管了，因为我的常规大脑吓坏了，我对他说：‘你知道这首歌吗？那我们走吧！这是一个小帐篷，之后感觉非常史诗般。我吓坏了。”</p><p>他继续说道：“我不得不直接回到公交车上，躺在地板上思考：‘到底发生了什么？我现在在俱乐部吗？我现在可以获得卡片或徽章吗？在<a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury">格拉斯顿伯</a>里与布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀一起演奏后，我至少应该获得一张 Nando 的黑卡！”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-gaslight-anthems-heavy-cover-of-billie-eilishs-ocean-eyes-3608361">《Listen to The Gaslight Anthem》对 Billie Eilish 的《Ocean Eyes》的厚重翻唱的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
